{"tid":1146025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷2件UNIQLO衫　休班警圖自殺留醫未能應訊","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:49:28.000Z","uid":86509,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a387bb1bcac054439a98a47a7c5f63411e112b3c","tid":1146025,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/mobile/bkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190507%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYfxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=7a6d933d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190507/mobile/bkn-20190507112754940-0507_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一名休班男警昨日(6日)涉嫌在觀塘apm商場店舖偷竊2件總值128港元的衣服，其後接受警員查問時又涉不合作而被捕。他被控以一項盜竊及一項抗拒警務人員罪，原定今日(7日)由警車押解往觀塘法院提訊，惟控方指被告曾試圖自殺，現正留院，暫未能應訊。裁判官遂將案件暫時押後至5月10日提訊，若被告出院將提早帶到法庭應訊，押後期間被告繼續羈押。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報稱警務人員的50歲被告劉志富，被控在今年5月6日於觀塘創紀之城第五期apm三樓一間店舖，偷竊一件價值49港元的白色童裝背心，及一件價值79港元的白色童裝T恤，合共總值128港元，上述物品為UNIQLO財產。劉另被控同日同地抗拒執行職責的警員陳志領。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a86084e1786df63dd6544343f5cc152f8101bec","tid":1146025,"uid":86509,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"撐警大聯盟去咗邊？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeff59c6249c5d7179a5a2093eaa9cd3226aba4","tid":1146025,"uid":121259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"究竟係咪香港做警察揾唔到食? 定係佢哋拉得人多, 想試吓比人拉呢?"},{"pid":"594f8f603e432c75864f72c1cba2525d0382279c","tid":1146025,"uid":838,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"爭條lan線"},{"pid":"58